# Trivy vulnerability IDs (CVE-... or GHSA-...) accepted as risk here, one
# per line, WITH A REASON — never add an entry without one. Read by both
# the "Dependency & Filesystem Scan" and "Docker Image Scan" Jenkins
# stages (trivy fs --ignorefile / trivy image --ignorefile point here).
#
# Example (remove once a real accepted CVE exists):
# CVE-2023-00000   # affects a dev-only transitive dep, not present in the runtime image; re-review by 2026-12-31
